2025-05-03 14:29:03.091 +07:00 [INF] Executed action DMCheckSheetAPI.Controllers.CheckSheetController.GetListCheckSheet (DMCheckSheetAPI) in 6.2033ms
2025-05-03 14:29:03.091 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (12ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
                                c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
                                c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        WHERE r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

SELECT [c].[SheetId], [c].[CancelFlag], [c].[CreateAt], [c].[CreateBy], [c].[FormNO], [c].[SheetCode], [c].[SheetName], [c].[UpdateAt], [c].[UpdateBy]

2025-05-03 14:29:05.978 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
                                c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
                                c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        WHERE r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

SELECT TOP(1) [d].[FullName], [d].[Id], [d].[Name], [d].[RoleId], [d].[UserName]
FROM (
    SELECT u.Id, u.UserName, u.FullName, u.PasswordHash, r.Id as RoleId, r.Name FROM AspNetUsers as u
                                LEFT JOIN AspNetUserRoles as ur ON u.Id = ur.UserId 
                                LEFT JOIN AspNetRoles as r ON ur.RoleId = r.Id

) AS [d]

2025-05-04 10:46:24.424 +07:00 [INF] Executing OkObjectResult, writing value of type 'DMCheckSheetAPI.Models.ApiResponse`1[[System.Collections.Generic.List`1[[DMCheckSheetAPI.Models.Domain.CheckSheetMST, DMCheckSheetAPI, Version=1.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=null]], System.Private.CoreLib, Version=8.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=7cec85d7bea7798e]]'.
2025-05-04 10:46:24.429 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
                                c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
                                c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        WHERE r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

Executing controller action with signature System.Threading.Tasks.Task`1[Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.IActionResult] GetListItemBySheetCode(System.String) on controller DMCheckSheetAPI.Controllers.CheckSheetItemController (DMCheckSheetAPI).
2025-05-04 11:14:56.006 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (8ms) [Parameters=[@SheetCode='?' (Size = 4)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

2025-05-04 11:15:15.688 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@SheetCode='?' (Size = 4)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

2025-05-04 11:24:45.528 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@SheetCode='?' (Size = 4)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

2025-05-04 11:26:19.055 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@SheetCode='?' (Size = 4)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

2025-05-04 11:26:32.646 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[@SheetCode='?' (Size = 4)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

2025-05-04 11:36:08.463 +07:00 [INF] Executed action DMCheckSheetAPI.Controllers.CheckSheetDeviceController.GetByDeviceAndCheckSheetCode (DMCheckSheetAPI) in 8.6273ms
2025-05-04 11:36:08.464 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@SheetCode='?' (Size = 4)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

Executing controller action with signature System.Threading.Tasks.Task`1[Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.IActionResult] GetListItemBySheetCode(System.String) on controller DMCheckSheetAPI.Controllers.CheckSheetItemController (DMCheckSheetAPI).
2025-05-04 11:38:03.616 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (8ms) [Parameters=[@SheetCode='?' (Size = 4)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag

2025-05-04 12:49:44.086 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@SheetCode='?' (Size = 4)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

2025-05-04 12:49:47.858 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@SheetCode='?' (Size = 4)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

2025-05-04 12:50:07.178 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@SheetCode='?' (Size = 4)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

2025-05-04 12:50:46.963 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (12ms) [Parameters=[@SheetCode='?' (Size = 4)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

2025-05-04 12:50:52.973 +07:00 [INF] Request finished HTTP/1.1 GET http://localhost:5118/api/CheckSheetDevice/checkSheetItemList?deviceCode=DV08&checkSheetCode=CS01 - 200 null application/json; charset=utf-8 28.7558ms
2025-05-04 12:50:52.975 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@SheetCode='?' (Size = 4)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;
2025-05-04 12:50:52.979 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (3ms) [Parameters=[@__sheetCode_0='?' (Size = 4000), @__deviceCode_1='?' (Size = 255), @__today_Date_2='?' (DbType = DateTime2)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [c].[ItemId], [c].[ResultId], [c].[Value], [c].[IsConfirmNG]
FROM [CheckResults] AS [c]
WHERE [c].[SheetCode] = @__sheetCode_0 AND [c].[DeviceCode] = @__deviceCode_1 AND CONVERT(date, [c].[CheckedDate]) = @__today_Date_2

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

2025-05-04 12:51:21.297 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@SheetCode='?' (Size = 4)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

2025-05-04 12:52:19.612 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@SheetCode='?' (Size = 4)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

2025-05-04 12:52:31.082 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@SheetCode='?' (Size = 4)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

2025-05-04 12:53:23.901 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@SheetCode='?' (Size = 4)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

2025-05-04 12:55:22.493 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@SheetCode='?' (Size = 4)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

2025-05-04 12:55:55.589 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@SheetCode='?' (Size = 4)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

SELECT [c].[SheetId], [c].[CancelFlag], [c].[CreateAt], [c].[CreateBy], [c].[FormNO], [c].[SheetCode], [c].[SheetName], [c].[UpdateAt], [c].[UpdateBy]
FROM [CheckSheetMST] AS [c]

2025-05-04 12:56:40.432 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
                                c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
                                c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        WHERE r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

2025-05-04 12:56:52.098 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[@SheetCode='?' (Size = 4)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

2025-05-04 12:56:57.238 +07:00 [INF] Route matched with {action = "GetResultsBySheetAndDate", controller = "CheckResult"}. Executing controller action with signature System.Threading.Tasks.Task`1[Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.IActionResult] GetResultsBySheetAndDateAsync(System.String, System.String, System.DateTime) on controller DMCheckSheetAPI.Controllers.CheckResultController (DMCheckSheetAPI).
2025-05-04 12:56:57.240 +07:00 [INF] Executed endpoint 'DMCheckSheetAPI.Controllers.CheckSheetDeviceController.GetByDeviceAndCheckSheetCode (DMCheckSheetAPI)'
2025-05-04 12:56:57.240 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@SheetCode='?' (Size = 4)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0

2025-05-04 15:30:38.545 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (26ms) [Parameters=[@SheetCode='?' (Size = 4)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

                            WITH RecursiveCheckSheet AS (
                            -- Lấy danh sách cha (ParentId IS NULL)
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                0 AS Level,
                                CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN CheckSheetMST cs ON c.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                            WHERE c.ParentId IS NULL AND cs.SheetCode = @SheetCode

                            UNION ALL

                            -- Lấy danh sách con và tiếp tục tạo thứ tự OrderPath
                            SELECT 
                                c.SheetId,
                                c.ItemId, 
                                c.ParentId, 
                                c.Content, 
		                        c.OrderNumber,
                                c.DataType,
                                c.CancelFlag,
                                rc.Level + 1, 
                                CAST(rc.Path + '.' + CAST(c.ItemId AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS Path,
                                CAST(rc.OrderPath + '.' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY c.SheetId, c.ParentId ORDER BY c.OrderNumber) AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 3) AS VARCHAR(MAX)) AS OrderPath
                            FROM CheckSheetItemMST c
                            INNER JOIN RecursiveCheckSheet rc ON c.ParentId = rc.ItemId
                        )
                        SELECT 
                            cs.SheetId, cs.FormNO, cs.SheetCode, cs.SheetName, r.ItemId, r.ParentId, r.Content, r.OrderNumber, r.DataType, r.Level, r.OrderPath, r.CancelFlag
                        FROM RecursiveCheckSheet as r
                        LEFT JOIN CheckSheetMST as cs ON r.SheetId = cs.SheetId
                        Where r.CancelFlag = 0
                        ORDER BY r.SheetId, r.OrderPath;

SELECT ra.ActionId, cr.ResultId,  cr.SheetCode, cr.SheetName, cr.DeviceCode, cr.DeviceName, cr.CheckedDate, ct.Content, cr.CheckedBy, ra.ActionTaken, ra.ActionDate, ra.ConfirmedBy, ra.ConfirmedDate, ra.Note, cr.[Value]  from ResultActions as ra
                              LEFT JOIN CheckResults AS cr ON ra.ResultId = cr.ResultId
                              LEFT JOIN CheckSheetItemMST AS ct ON cr.ItemId = ct.ItemId
